<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Operator on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/operator/</link><description>Recent content in Operator on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/operator/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Dart Null Check Operator Used on Null Value — Runtime Error Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/null-check/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/null-check/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="null-check-operator-used-on-null-value--runtime-error-fix"&gt;Null Check Operator Used on Null Value — Runtime Error Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;Null check operator used on a null value&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when you use the &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; (null check) operator on a variable that is actually &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt;. This is a runtime exception in Dart&amp;rsquo;s null safety system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Dart&amp;rsquo;s null-safe mode, the &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; operator asserts that a value is non-null and forces it into a non-nullable type. If the value is &lt;code&gt;null&lt;/code&gt; at runtime, Dart throws a &lt;code&gt;LateInitializationError&lt;/code&gt; or a &lt;code&gt;TypeError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;Null check operator used on a null value&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python SyntaxError — Walrus Operator Invalid Syntax</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/walrus-operator/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/walrus-operator/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="syntaxerror--walrus-operator-invalid-syntax"&gt;SyntaxError — Walrus Operator Invalid Syntax&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;SyntaxError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;invalid syntax&amp;rdquo; when using the walrus operator &lt;code&gt;:=&lt;/code&gt; is raised when you use this operator in a context where it&amp;rsquo;s not allowed, or when using it in Python versions before 3.8. The walrus operator was introduced in Python 3.8 (PEP 572).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The walrus operator &lt;code&gt;:=&lt;/code&gt; allows assignment expressions inside other expressions. It assigns a value to a variable as part of a larger expression. However, it has restrictions: it cannot be used at the top level, in function arguments (in some contexts), or in certain other positions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Null check operator used on null</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/null-check-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/null-check-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;Null check operator used on null value&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when you use the &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; (null check) operator on a value that is null. This operator asserts that the value is non-null, but if it is null, a &lt;code&gt;TypeError&lt;/code&gt; is thrown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using &lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt; on nullable variables without null check&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assuming Future result is non-null&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Database or API returning null&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing null-aware operators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Using ! on nullable value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.length); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Null check error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use null check or default
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;.length &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// or
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(name.length);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Assuming Future result is non-null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Future&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; future &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fetchData();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; future.then((v) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; v&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Null check error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Handle null in Future
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Future&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; future &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; fetchData();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; future &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;default&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dart" data-lang="dart"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Null variable
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; s &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; len &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; s&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.length; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Null check operator used on null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Map access
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Map&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; map &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; map[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;key&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Null check error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Function return
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; findUser(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; id) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; findUser(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;99&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;.toUpperCase(); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Null check error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/type-cast-error"&gt;type cast error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/dart/state-error4"&gt;StateError: No element&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>